      <title>特朗普呼吁苹果解密刺客手机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-calls-on-apple-to-decrypt-phones-of-would-be-assassins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普呼吁苹果公司协助联邦调查人员获取两名被控密谋暗杀他的男子的手机和应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-calls-on-apple-to-decrypt-phones-of-would-be-assassins</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:41:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与盟国合作制止黎巴嫩以色列与真主党的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正与法国和英国等盟友合作，提出一项旨在阻止以色列军队与黎巴嫩真主党武装分子之间冲突升级的提案。此次冲突已造成数百人死亡，并有可能引发更大范围的中东冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京扩大核战略以应对西方“侵略”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/putin-broadens-nuclear-doctrine-to-counter-western-aggression</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京表示，俄罗斯将修改其核政策，以应对其他核大国支持的无核国家的“侵略”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/putin-broadens-nuclear-doctrine-to-counter-western-aggression</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:21:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的盟友敦促他在早期摇摆不定之后掌控局面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/starmer-s-allies-urge-him-to-get-control-after-early-wobbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当基尔·斯塔默在工党年度会议上努力向工党成员保证其“冷静、坚定”的领导能力时，利物浦的高级助手和议员们却在幕后私下敲响警钟，敦促他振作起来，因为他上任伊始就经历了动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/starmer-s-allies-urge-him-to-get-control-after-early-wobbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基争取支持的努力遭遇美国竞选紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-s-push-for-support-runs-into-us-campaign-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统竞选活动升温，总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基本周呼吁美国加大对乌克兰抵抗俄罗斯入侵的支持，此举引发了美国政坛动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/zelenskiy-s-push-for-support-runs-into-us-campaign-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 16:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰总理称苹果税收优惠将用于住房和能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/apple-tax-boon-to-go-toward-housing-energy-irish-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰总理西蒙·哈里斯表示，爱尔兰将把最近苹果公司法庭裁决征收的近 140 亿欧元（156 亿美元）的税款专门用于住房、能源和水利基础设施建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/apple-tax-boon-to-go-toward-housing-energy-irish-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 16:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚竞争对手就任命央行行长达成妥协</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/libya-rivals-agree-on-interim-central-bank-chief-lawmaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国称，利比亚各派就任命欧佩克成员国央行新领导层达成“妥协”，这是最终解决导致石油产量大幅下降的危机的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/libya-rivals-agree-on-interim-central-bank-chief-lawmaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 16:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人口增长放缓 特鲁多移民计划受质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府削减移民数量，加拿大人口的快速增长正在逐渐减缓。然而，该国距离大幅减少临时居民的目标还有很长的路要走——而临时居民的数量现在比以往任何时候都要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 12:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿州长领跑者捍卫资本利得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/washington-governor-candidate-ferguson-defends-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿州州长候选人鲍勃·弗格森为该州的资本利得税辩护，强调其在资助教育方面发挥的重要作用，而共和党支持的投票倡议则试图废除该税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/washington-governor-candidate-ferguson-defends-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约学校校长班克斯将在联邦调查期间离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/new-york-schools-chancellor-banks-to-leave-amid-federal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市教育局长戴维·班克斯 (David Banks) 表示他将于 12 月 31 日退休，成为纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 政府中最新一位宣布离职计划的成员，因为目前至少有四起联邦腐败调查震动了市政厅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/new-york-schools-chancellor-banks-to-leave-amid-federal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 21:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
